page.title: 10A FAMILY OF BUCKHURST HILL
page.content: My dad is a doctor in Barts hospital in London. He is Welsh and was born in Blackpill,which is just outside Swansea. My mum is a senior-staff nurse at Holly House hospital in Buckhurst Hill. She works four times a week. My mum is allso a keen gardener. My sister is ten years old she is interested in art. Charlotte plays the violin and her teacher says she is talented. Our family often goes out to play cricet at weekeds . My dad is a demon-bowler. When we get home we have a mars which he buys at Brick Lane market. We also have to pets,a cat called Felix and a tortoise called Rodderick. Felix is a tabby tom. He is often in figths with other cats. Felix thouth is a softy. Rodderick is very large. He also likes been stroked.
